alert_template.description:
Employee reported a physical security concern. Escalate severity to HIGH if 'access_compromise_concern' indicates lost/stolen badge, lost/stolen device, unfamiliar device on network, or unauthorized presence in restricted area.

Reporter: {{reporter_email}}
When: {{when_happened}}
Location: {{location}}
Incident type: {{incident_type}}
Reporter engagement: {{did_you_engage}}
Access compromise concern: {{access_compromise_concern}}

Observation:
{{what_you_observed}}

Additional context:
{{additional_context}}

Photo attached: {{photo}}

Triage note: coordinate with facilities/physical security; pull badge access logs and CCTV for the location and time window; if device was found plugged in, isolate the port and treat as potential rogue device.
